criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Aged ≥18 years;

          -  Permanent residents of study provinces;

          -  Able and willing to provide informed consent to participate in the study;

          -  Able and willing to provide nasopharyngeal swab and venous blood sample;

          -  Able and willing to complete a questionnaire survey for collecting information on
             histories of COVID-19 vaccination and disease;

          -  Considered as suspected cases of SARS-CoV-2 infections by the physicians in the study
             clinics according to DR national protocol.

        Exclusion Criteria:

        -
